   1014
   1015                                 ; ------------------------------------------------------------
   1016                                 ; UDA50 INIT handshake
   1017                                 ; Four steps, each requiring:
   1018                                 ;   - Wait for RDY bit corresponding to current step mask
   1019                                 ;   - Write next word from table to CSR
   1020                                 ;   - Shift mask left
   1021                                 ; ------------------------------------------------------------
